<li>Verschueren, Jef, Jan-Ola Östman, Jan Blommaert, eds. (1995) <i>Handbook of Pragmatics</i>. Amsterdam: Benjamins.</li>
<li>Watzlawick, Paul, Janet Helmick Beavin and Don D. Jackson (1967) <i>Pragmatics of Human Communication: A Study of Interactional Patterns, Pathologies, and Paradoxes</i>. New York: Norton.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Anna_Wierzbicka" title="Anna Wierzbicka">Wierzbicka, Anna</a> (1991) <i>Cross-cultural Pragmatics. The Semantics of Human Interaction</i>. Berlin, New York: Mouton de Gruyter.</li>
<li>Yule, George (1996) <i>Pragmatics</i> (Oxford Introductions to Language Study). Oxford University Press.</li>
<li>Silverstein, Michael. 1976. "Shifters, Linguistic Categories, and Cultural Description," in Meaning and Anthropology, Basso and Selby, eds. New York: Harper &amp; Row</li>
<li>Mey, Jacob. (2001). "Pragmatics: An Introduction". Blackwell.</li>
<li>Wardhaugh, Ronald. (2006). "An Introduction to Sociolinguistics". Blackwell.</li>
<li>Duranti, Alessandro. (1997). "Linguistic Anthropology". Cambridge University Press.</li>
<li>Carbaugh, Donal. (1990). "Cultural Communication and Intercultural Contact." LEA.</li>
</ul>
<p><br /></p>
